name: Delosperma cooperi - Hardy iceplant | Celebrating 1k followers on Twitter
description:
Hello dear Fam, 

What a huge start in 2022!

To celebrate reaching 1k followers on Twitter, Im so happy to share with this NFT for you. Since I got in the NFT world second time (firstly I joined dec 20' and gave a break, then a year later dec 21' I joined the game), I met so many great artists and collectors, joined amazing commmunities. Hope things are gonna go well in 2022.



Huge thank you to everyone! LFG!


Sincerely,
H.I. Cetinkaya
